description: This trap is sent each time a threshold on a PM condition
on an PTP Network Probe is crossed.
objects.test: $SNMPTRAPCMD F3-SYNCJACK-MIB::f3SyncJPTPNetworkProbeThresholdCrossingAlert F3-SYNCJACK-MIB::f3SyncJPTPNetworkProbeThresholdIndex i 9999 F3-SYNCJACK-MIB::f3SyncJPTPNetworkProbeThresholdInterval i 1 F3-SYNCJACK-MIB::f3SyncJPTPNetworkProbeThresholdVariable o 1.3.6.1.4.1.8072.2.1.1 F3-SYNCJACK-MIB::f3SyncJPTPNetworkProbeThresholdValueLo u 9999 F3-SYNCJACK-MIB::f3SyncJPTPNetworkProbeThresholdValueHi u 9999 F3-SYNCJACK-MIB::f3SyncJPTPNetworkProbeThresholdMonValue C 9999

description: An index that uniquely identifies an entry in the
f3SyncJPTPNetworkProbeThresholdTable.
variables.name: F3-SYNCJACK-MIB::f3SyncJPTPNetworkProbeThresholdIndex

description: The interval over which monitored value is
sampled and compared with the specified threshold.
variables.name: F3-SYNCJACK-MIB::f3SyncJPTPNetworkProbeThresholdInterval

description: The object identifier of the particular variable to be
sampled.
variables.name: F3-SYNCJACK-MIB::f3SyncJPTPNetworkProbeThresholdVariable

description: Lower 32 bits of the threshold value.
variables.name: F3-SYNCJACK-MIB::f3SyncJPTPNetworkProbeThresholdValueLo

description: Higher 32 bits of the threshold value.
variables.name: F3-SYNCJACK-MIB::f3SyncJPTPNetworkProbeThresholdValueHi

description: Monitored value corresponding to f3SyncJPTPNetworkProbeThresholdVariable.
variables.name: F3-SYNCJACK-MIB::f3SyncJPTPNetworkProbeThresholdMonValue
